CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published  in the Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 21, 1963, pg. 16 reads: "Dynamic Danettes - Voicing their intention to make each one of their club members an NAACP life member, the Dynamic Danet[t]es Civic CLub is busy making plans to raise more funds.  Left to right: Treasurer Margaret Nelson, General Chairman Florence Hutchinson, Secretary Gladys Brown, Audelle Wade, Delores Woodfork, Vice President Gladys Lawson, Betty Culberson, Jesse Grogan and President Ida Jones. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Two frames: Portrait of Margaret Nelson wearing dark silk shantung dress and necklace with large beads; Portrait of Audelle Wade wearing dark shirt and four strand beaded necklace
